# Allowlist-style .gitignore: everything is ignored by default, and only
# specific files/directories are explicitly un-ignored below. This folder
# has a lot of large reference material and personal data that must never
# be committed (especially since this repo is public) -- safer to opt files
# IN one at a time than to try to opt everything else OUT.

# Deny everything at the root by default.
/*

# Allow looking inside these directories (see per-directory rules below).
!/code/
!/Photos/
!/.gitignore

# Reviewed by Jim and confirmed clean of personal/sensitive info (Jul 2 2026).
!/Acton Bounds TODO.md

# Jim removed Email/Phone columns from Contacts and re-exported (Jul 2 2026);
# verified clean of emails/phone numbers/Drive-Sheet IDs before allowlisting.
!/Acton Bounds.xlsx

# Reviewed and approved by Jim (Jul 3 2026) -- Project Notes.md's town clerk
# contact table is public government office info, not personal.
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/Project Notes.md

# Jim committed this directly via GitHub's web UI (Jul 3 2026); added here
# so it's reflected in the allowlist too.
!/README.md

# --- code/ ---
/code/*
!/code/*.py
!/code/claude.md
!/code/.python-version
!/code/requirements.txt

# --- Photos/ ---
/Photos/*
!/Photos/process_takeout.py
!/Photos/CLAUDE.md
!/Photos/requirements.txt
!/Photos/.python-version
!/Photos/Acton Bounds - SiteNames.csv
